name mp-geom2d
category Package
revision 77019
shortdesc Flat geometry with MetaPost
longdesc This package was written with the aim of providing MetaPost
longdesc macros for creating a geometry figure that closely matches an
longdesc imperative description: Let A be the point with coordinates
longdesc (2,3). Let B be the point with coordinates (4,5). Draw the line
longdesc (A, B). ...
